00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:49.119
Where am I?

00:02:49.119 --> 00:02:50.399
You’re finally awake.

00:02:50.399 --> 00:02:52.639
You fainted on the street again last night.

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:54.399
