00:07:46.959 --> 00:07:47.839
How is that possible?

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:49.440
You oversaw the execution today.

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:50.880
We saw Liu Chunru’s body

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:51.880
displayed after beheading.

00:07:51.880 --> 00:07:52.640
Now—

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:53.959
