00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:44.719
Ruizhi—

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.039
Ruizhi—

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.400
If you don’t believe me,

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:50.960
come and see for yourself.

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:08.119
She came back for her head.

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.119
If she can’t find her head,

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:11.840
