00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:54.599
The one inside—

00:10:54.919 --> 00:10:55.599
Who is she?

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:59.599
She’s a concubine of our household.

00:10:59.599 --> 00:11:01.320
